{"tid":2303350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺起源不在武漢  中国科學院：「原始病毒」來自印度","createTime":"2020-11-28T01:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T02:07:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c811e8d81c9dc507646f388f1cebd044a52743c2","tid":2303350,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:12:45.000Z","msg":"綜合外媒報導，中國科學院研究小組指出，和所有細胞一樣，病毒在繁殖時也會發生突變，這意味著病毒每次複製繁衍時，去氧核糖核酸（DNA）都會發生微小變化，因此可透過「找出突變最少的樣本」來追蹤原始版本的病毒；研究小組更直指武漢所發現的病毒並非「原始病毒」，原始病毒恐來自孟加拉、美國、希臘、澳洲、印度、義大利，捷克、俄羅斯及塞爾維亞其中一國。<br />\n<br />\n研究小組表示，由於印度和孟加拉都發現低突變的樣本，且都是中國的鄰近國家，因此第一次傳播很可能發生在這2國；透過估算病毒突變一次所需的時間，並將這時間與在印度和孟加拉採集到的樣本進行比較，該病毒最早於2019年7月或8月於這2個國家出現。<br />\n<br />\n研究小組認為，印度中北部和巴基斯坦皆發生熱浪，使得水資源匱乏，諸如猴子之類的野生動物，為了水源會進行爭奪地盤等行為，勢必增加了人與野生動物互動的機會，因此「我們推測，新冠病毒由動物傳人，可能與這異常的熱浪有關」。<br />\n<br />\n研究小組最後表示，因為印度醫療體系較差，加上其國年輕人口染疫後症狀較輕微，才令這種病毒在數個月難以被發現，從而四處傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20201128edi002/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20201128edi002%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ClznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=25daf0e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20201128edi002/</a>"},{"pid":"f5a1d4fe6138dba1be4a6770a5b1b62b30c5a728","tid":2303350,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"責任全在x方"},{"pid":"382f3f12d1c402dba2c41794eaf07b5d749e3526","tid":2303350,"uid":366652,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:17:30.000Z","msg":"個病毒來自Anywhere but China<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得啦得啦 唔係中國起源<br />\n但係係o係武漢失控 咁得未?<br />\n但係都無用啦 都過左咁耐 咩證據都比中國消滅晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab4d3fa9ab9bbe89add0bdc55e73a21ac26cfa5","tid":2303350,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"期待下次作篇武漢肺炎來源自外太空生物"},{"pid":"5971c3271c45a2b8781123ec602a0046c54aafac","tid":2303350,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:23:52.000Z","msg":"美國，意大利，然後到印度，總之唔係中國起源 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee175bf12b7d45482a8ff1f4e98dadf4a69c7d3","tid":2303350,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"好耐之前喺Twitter睇到呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TrXobn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TrXobn.jpg&h=b3e345cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LYVX7C3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLYVX7C3.jpg&h=c7a4de0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4728ed8304c16720f78b6c38f852b78114af2be1","tid":2303350,"uid":254123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"原始病毒可能唔係黎自中國<br />\n<br />\n但武肺係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">合成病毒</span></span>"},{"pid":"41957012b6a14cba4f970f2bbef860bf0ae3b80b","tid":2303350,"uid":344173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:28:24.000Z","msg":"西班牙流感都唔係起源於西班牙都俾人叫足百幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce49d4128392af5f119b3762ffff01236943075","tid":2303350,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"冇左made in hong kong  所以今次唔屈落香港到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac01feb88b4e236cb2e2483ea44d23a05229f27","tid":2303350,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"咁點解蝗國放武漢班垃圾出去之後其他地方先爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8425dce46c18e08b597696d4128ed56e8a8bdf51","tid":2303350,"uid":271807,"like":1,"disl